Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:09.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:13.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:17.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:21.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Siegrain and Jellal were a single person!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:27.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Etherion was unleashed, and the true \Nform of the Tower of Heaven was revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:31.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to be her usual self when \Nshe wakes up from this nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:33.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I will fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:10.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Natsu and Erza are okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:15.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're fine. Because they're \Nboth Fairy Tail wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:19.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got that right. All we \Ncan do now is believe in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:29.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all fired up! More than I've ever been!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:33.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end this in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:37.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you to Hell regretting the \Nfact that you ever stood up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:41.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One thing I know is that \NI can be real stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:43.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna do it, then \Ngive me your best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:47.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:12.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Titania Falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:17.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:24.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? That all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:27.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared a breakin' the \Ntower, so you're holding back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:28.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't gonna work on me, bub!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:32.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't gonna talk so \Nbig for long, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:36.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dazzling Blaze of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's... the tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:02.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The tower I spent 8 years constructing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:03.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:09.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what a {\i1}shame{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:13.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, remember? My \Nspecialty is destroying stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:18.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... He can barely even stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:20.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:33.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this magical \Npower? It's making me sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadows are extending \Nbackwards to the light source!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:38.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! This magic is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:43.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall into the infinite \Ndarkness, dragon wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:45.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you let me be killed as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:01.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You need a body to resurrect Zeref, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:06.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a general requirement \Nthat the body be of a wizard
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:09.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,about as powerful as one \Nof the Ten Wizard Saints.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:15.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But at this point, it doesn't \Nhave to be you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:17.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Die together, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:27.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavenly Body Magic:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Altairis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:39.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:51.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're okay... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sho, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this unsettled feeling I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:12.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:22.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:27.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:33.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still crawling around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:35.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You worm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:37.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:38.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:45.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:48.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:51.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...of help...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:55.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,..to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:56.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...at last...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:07:01.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand! Now, no more talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...always...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...so kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...so kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:14.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:32.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...ed you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:17.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How pointless! How incredibly pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They call that throwing \Naway your life, Simon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't change a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:26.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there's no way anyone \Nis leaving this tower alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:40.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:45.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The crazy bastard is eating Etherion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:11.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:15.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ethernano is fused with other \Nelements than fire, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:21.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you seriously think you could power up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,by eating such powerful magic \Nenergy instead of flames?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:27.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of peabrained thinking \Nwill lead you to your own downfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:49.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's actually absorbing Etherion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:01.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...that Erza is crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:05.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:08.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, take care of Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You cocky bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:14.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:24.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be able to \Ncatch me at this speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:39.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:44.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making a kingdom of freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:49.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref whispered to me in my pain and fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:54.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you desire true freedom?" \NZeref beckoned...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:58.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Only I can sense Zeref!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:01.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the chosen one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:05.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref and I will create a \Ntruly free kingdom together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:09.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll make it by taking \Naway other people's freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:15.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only ones with the will to change \Nthe world can make history!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:18.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you understand this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:24.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Abyss Break?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:28.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend! You plan to \Ndestroy the tower as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,8 more years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:34.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... This time I'll finish it in 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:45.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will never find freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:51.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no such thing as freedom \Nfor somebody taken over by ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:57.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Free yourself first, Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:18.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's got to be Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:27.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, is that gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:30.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay... Or so I'd like to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:32.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But he sure is going wild there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:53.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Natsu's true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:58.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...a Dragon Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He even defeated Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:34.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle I've been fighting \Nthese 8 years is now over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:39.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everyone is truly free...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:42.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:13:59.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:06.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:11.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel a terrible magical \Npower coming from that light!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:13.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:16.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could Etherion be going out of control?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of control? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magical power of Etherion...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:28.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping that great amount of magical power \Nin one place can never be stable for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:31.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A turbulent vortex of magical power with \Nno where else to go will burst out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,causing a giant explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:37.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! We'll be caught in it as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:38.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Sister and \Nthe others still inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:43.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't about who's saving who anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:46.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all going to be wiped out together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:14:59.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:34.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical power strong enough to deform \Nthe container... The lacrima...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:37.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's even more destructive \Npower than I had imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:42.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we get outside, we'll \Nbe caught up in the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:44.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:57.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... There's no way I'll give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:01.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's my turn to save you, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:06.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's impossible to hold it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:12.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The tremendous amount of magical \Npower this lacrima now stores,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:15.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,will be fused into your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:21.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body will be deconstructed, and \Nthen reconstituted into Zeref's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fused?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:30.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can fuse with Etherion, then can I \Ncontrol this power? Can I stop the explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:38.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to take the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:48.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. The lacrima is still accepting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:16:59.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:04.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:09.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza... You're putting \Nyourself into the lacrima?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:13.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only way to stop Etherion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:16.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop Etherion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Look around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:25.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This tower will shortly explode \Nas Etherion goes out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:30.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I can fuse with \NEtherion and suppress it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:36.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:41.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop it for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:44.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:47.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:54.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:06.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have lived without Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:11.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A world without my friends is unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:18.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are all just that important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:21.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can save everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:33.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...then I do so without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:35.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it takes this body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...so be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:48.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of there, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:52.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, take care of everyone for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:58.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'll always be by your side...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exploding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:17.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:22.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Etherion is heading up into the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:40.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Etherion went into the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:43.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza! Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:20:00.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a horrid wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:03.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be quite difficult \Nfor you to see again, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:07.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now... I'm asking you \Nnicely so no complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:12.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got such a pretty face, \Nhave some compassion would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:16.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Owwww!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:20.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not thinking of laying hands \Non her when she's older, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:23.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:27.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:30.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rob was helping her out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:32.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rob?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.32,0:20:33.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:37.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:00.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:12.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:14.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:16.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:19.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then get out, immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:21.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate humans, get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:25.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's healed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:32.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... That eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only crying out of one eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That shouldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:44.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't make an error\Nwhile mixing the medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:45.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:47.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:54.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already cried out \Nhalf my tears, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:05.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.73,0:24:00.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, it seems like our new \Nguild is finally finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.09,0:24:02.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! I can't wait to check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.77,0:24:06.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally been rebuilt, so don't go \Ndestroying it all of a sudden, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.72,0:24:10.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, since when have I been the \Ntype to go around destroying stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.73,0:24:13.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he that oblivious? Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:15.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Home!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:19.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Things break because Gray \Nand Erza go crazy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.71,0:24:22.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's usually you who \Nstarts the fights, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.31,0:24:24.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's all my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.05,0:24:26.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
